des: WHVO plays the best hits from the 50's, 60's, and 70's. As a matter of fact, we play the very songs that were the original rock and roll hits heard on 1480 AM, Hopkinsville's first rock and roll station. WHVO's News Edge Team provides more local news than any other radio or TV station in our listening area. WHVO is the home of Fort Campbell Falcons football.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
